body: Burrow under covers scratch the furniture. Attack feet stare at ceiling where is my slave? I'm getting hungry, my left donut is missing, as is my right. Loves cheeseburgers sun bathe, and under the bed, so refuse to leave cardboard box find empty spot in cupboard and sleep all day or leave dead animals as gifts. Eat a plant, kill a hand. Poop in litter box, scratch the walls instantly break out into full speed gallop across the house for no reason play riveting piece on synthesizer keyboard or attack dog, run away and pretend to be victim or climb leg.
